    "title": "襲来！二大魔将",
    "enTitle": "Demon Generals Attack!",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――ウマネスト大陸辺境『魔王城』",
            "enText": "In a remote region of the continent of Uma Nest \nlooms the castle of the demon lord.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": -4558863469033238397,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ王ゴルシ",
            "enName": "Horse Lord Golshi",
            "jpText": "いやー食った食った！　やっぱ未来を棒に振って食う\r\n種籾のリゾットは最高だな！",
            "enText": "Man, that was tasty! Nothing beats ruining \nan entire civilization for a bowl of risotto!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 270,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "pathId": -5280945727914516192,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ王ゴルシ",
            "enName": "Horse Lord Golshi",
            "jpText": "にしても……どうすっか。エルとグラスか……。別のウマ娘さえ\r\n来なけりゃ、ずっとこのゴルシ様の天下だったのによー。",
            "enText": "Anyways… what am I going to do about El and Grass? \nI would've been unstoppable if they hadn't showed up.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 366,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "pathId": 5365460323484477256,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ王ゴルシ",
            "enName": "Horse Lord Golshi",
            "jpText": "この城に押しかけて来る前に、手打っとくか。\r\nおい、魔将Aに魔将B！",
            "enText": "I better get prepared before they barge their way into my castle.\nHey, Demon General A! Demon General B!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "pathId": -4757210304048288862,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "魔将2人",
            "enName": "Demon Generals",
            "jpText": "お呼びですか、魔王様。",
            "enText": "How can we serve you, your demonic lordship?",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": -775171436690093653,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ王ゴルシ",
            "enName": "Horse Lord Golshi",
            "jpText": "『魔王』じゃねえ。間違えんな。\r\n『ウマ王』だ、『ウマ王』！",
            "enText": "It's <i>Gold</i> Ship, got it? The Horse Lord Gold Ship!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 177,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "pathId": 6274949659133908652,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ王ゴルシ",
            "enName": "Horse Lord Golshi",
            "jpText": "おいテメエら、格闘家エルと治癒士グラスの\r\nお尻ペンペンして、元の世界へ追い返してこい！",
            "enText": "Now listen up. Go and give that brawler El and her \ncleric Grass a good spanking and send 'em packing!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 221,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "pathId": -6945052718685980717,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "そうですか。魔王……いえ、ウマ王の正体はゴルシ先輩！\r\nそれがトラブルの元なら、一刻も早く倒さなければ。",
            "enText": "I see. The \"lordship\" that demon officer revered so much… \nis actually Gold Ship! If she's the cause of this recent trouble, \nwe'll need to take her out as soon as possible.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 471,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 156,
                    "pathId": -803736115371838908
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 2695499834567128320
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 187,
                    "pathId": -2023031497715128180
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": 6245330616457986318
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5377446552228653063,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "？？？",
            "enName": "???",
            "jpText": "おーっほっほっほ！\r\nそうはいかないわ、お2人さん！",
            "enText": "Ohohoho! I'm not about to let <i>that</i> happen!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 157,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 3458329923103021864
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": -7734754008913816157
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 2906273429024833780
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 69,
                    "pathId": -4543507831378189745
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2890117418307593785,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "あなたたちはこの場で倒されるの。\r\nウマ王さまに仕える一流魔将、この『キングレイジョー』に。",
            "enText": "You're going to meet your end right here, right now. \nAs the Horse Lord's first-rate general, I, Madam King, \nwill make sure of it!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 329,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -2835503790072921009
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 2431955168480848726
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 155,
                    "pathId": 8652981259147617792
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 19,
                    "pathId": -8541403022509994398
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 157,
                    "pathId": 5273444405132066740
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -981505661868511613
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4360427657533447613,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "キング……レイジョー！？\r\nキングちゃんをモデルに生み出された魔族でしょうか？",
            "enText": "Madam… King? A demon modeled after King Halo, I gather.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 277,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 151,
                    "pathId": -8886773394621296467
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 145,
                    "pathId": 2767630300720686018
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -5418060158384543374
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -3924543480810745101
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5175872225503027258,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "悪のレイジョー……。なんか放っておいても、\r\n勝手に破滅しそうデース……。",
            "enText": "An evil King… let's just ignore her. \nShe'll probably fall to ruin all on her own.",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 225,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 249,
                    "pathId": -9002962562420158390
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 233,
                    "pathId": -3810415328466581086
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 111,
                    "pathId": 6535620723880115528
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 7176960104255536778
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7098557540475243751,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "失礼ねっ！　しないわ、破滅なんて！",
            "enText": "How rude! I will <i>not</i> fall to ruin in any way!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 106,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -5469583608811427266
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 252,
                    "pathId": 7672145388566419717
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": 6187645339109339513
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6947411479139699184,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "それに魔将はもう1人いるのよ。\r\nほら、ごらんなさい。この空模様を……。",
            "enText": "I should warn you though, I'm not the only general here \nto thwart your little plans. Take a look up at the sky.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 274,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 239,
                    "pathId": 3010152590401164069
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": 5937878830441412615
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 168,
                    "pathId": 7217824139757801334
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 43,
                    "pathId": 6850601389463616291
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -4342640994590130092
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 3520719258145862164
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8551747458877313249,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "――！？\r\n急に暗雲が……。これは……？",
            "enText": "…<i>!</i>? Where did those dark clouds come from all of a sudden…?",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 128,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -3810988702724303509
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 16,
                    "pathId": -8647561913441780780
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 2788128515262592956
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -1510906514563623272
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": -5082822954049893175
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 13,
                    "pathId": 7761459745410079243
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8442996550983014421,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "おーっほっほ！　魔族の中には天候を自由に操れる者もいる。\r\nもう1人の魔将は、この子よ！",
            "enText": "Ohohoho! Some demons are able to manipulate \nthe weather to their liking. It just so happens that \nmy fellow general is one such demon!",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 332,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "pathId": 388193261004368522,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ブラッディスカイ",
            "enName": "Bloody Sky",
            "jpText": "ふふふふ、私は闇のドルイド『ブラッディスカイ』。\r\nセイウンじゃないので、お間違えなきよう～。",
            "enText": "Hehehe. I'm the dark druid, Bloody Sky. \nThe peaceful Sky you love is about to disappear forever!",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 304,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "pathId": -1432898201848784879,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ブラッディスカイ",
            "enName": "Bloody Sky",
            "jpText": "さあ、鮮血色の雲よ！\r\n世界を真っ赤に染めつくすのだー。",
            "enText": "Come, crimson clouds! Bathe this world in red!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 214,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "pathId": 5729727278135209097,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "な、なんか空の色が気味悪くなったデース！\r\nおぇぇぇ……。",
            "enText": "Th-the sky's starting to look all dark and gloomy! Oh no…",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 198,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "pathId": 7416103166572462165,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "グラスワンダー",
            "enName": "Grass Wonder",
            "jpText": "気をつけて、エル！\r\n次はどんな術を繰り出してくるか……！",
            "enText": "Be careful, El! We don't know what \nkind of magic they'll cast next…!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 159,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "pathId": 3681158151684534262,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ブラッディスカイ",
            "enName": "Bloody Sky",
            "jpText": "ふ、ふ、ふふふふふ……！",
            "enText": "Hehehehehe!",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "pathId": -3375976783088471494,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ブラッディスカイ",
            "enName": "Bloody Sky",
            "jpText": "って、これしかできないんだけどね～。\r\n空の色を変えるだけだったりして。",
            "enText": "I mean, changing the sky's color is pretty much \nthe extent of my abilities.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 189,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "pathId": 4285365934610186813,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ブラッディスカイ",
            "enName": "Bloody Sky",
            "jpText": "でもほら、だいぶ雰囲気は出たから。\r\nってことでキング、あとよろ～。",
            "enText": "But still, it really set the mood, huh? \nYou can take it from here, King!",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 181,
            "voiceIdx": 21,
            "pathId": -2352367314735405451,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "えええっ、また途中で丸投げ！？　いつもいつもあなたは……。\r\n……コホン、ではここからは私が。",
            "enText": "Huh? Passing the buck before the deed is done again? \nWhy are you always… Oh… Ahem… Where were we?",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 344,
            "voiceIdx": 22,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 125,
                    "pathId": 8765173167607043212
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -781491802010200797
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 120,
                    "pathId": 3211381029539831826
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 417,
                    "pathId": 5044357145921547677
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 37,
                    "pathId": -9005262101287124889
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4172644992625806189,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "さあ、エルさん。あなたを素敵な世界にご招待よぉ～。\r\n幻影魔法『キングスワールド』！",
            "enText": "Now then, El. Allow me to welcome you to my wonderful \nrealm of illusion and magic. Welcome to The King's World!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 297,
            "voiceIdx": 23,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 6477954707623340950
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5253652257292470216
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 230,
                    "pathId": -3344666946995687809
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -8850509498477055776
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 802520278541850066,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "ケ……？　ここは？",
            "enText": "Huh…? Where am I?",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "voiceIdx": 24,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 12,
                    "pathId": -3141188678091753374
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 12,
                    "pathId": -4167449001578521493
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 12,
                    "pathId": 1343546767248973675
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7369590462441306441,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "ごらんの通り、王城の舞踏会場よ。\r\n令嬢同士の勝負は、格闘ではなくダンスで行うもの。",
            "enText": "As you can surely see, this is the ballroom of my lordship's \nroyal palace. In this arena, we ladies will compete not by \ncombat, but through dance.",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 299,
            "voiceIdx": 25,
            "pathId": -7872080060426437645,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "私と踊ってくださいますこと、エルさん？\r\nソーシャルダンスぐらいできるでしょう？",
            "enText": "So, would you care to dance, El? \nSurely, you know a friendly social dance or two?",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "voiceIdx": 26,
            "pathId": -5021126971054581275,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "な、なななな、なんデスか、それ！\r\nエルエルの得意なダンスといえば……。",
            "enText": "A, a what?! I-I mean, I know <i>a</i> dance, sure…",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 214,
            "voiceIdx": 27,
            "pathId": -3349494803050608421,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "これデース！　マンボ、マンボ！\r\nチャッチャ、チャチャッチャチャ！　ウー！",
            "enText": "Check this out! Mambo! \nA-cha-cha-cha! Cha-cha-cha-cha! Woo!",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 207,
            "voiceIdx": 28,
            "pathId": 7840020560156260364,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "なぁに？　クセが強すぎて、まるで雪猿みたい。\r\nあなた、いつも『世界最強』とか吹聴してるけど、今の動きは……。",
            "enText": "What? Your moves are terrible. It's like watching a snow monkey \ntry to dance. You have the nerve to constantly boast about being \nthe world's strongest, but by the looks of it…",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 396,
            "voiceIdx": 29,
            "pathId": 297151655230297134,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "世界サイテーね！",
            "enText": "You're the world's <i>weakest</i> dancer!",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": 30,
            "pathId": 299501452293262406,
            "blockIdx": 32
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "ぐわあぁぁぁん！　世界サイテー！？",
            "enText": "Gahhhh! The world's… weakest?!",
            "nextBlock": 34,
            "origClipLength": 135,
            "voiceIdx": 31,
            "pathId": -3794200618497683022,
            "blockIdx": 33
        },
        {
            "jpName": "キングレイジョー",
            "enName": "Madam King",
            "jpText": "そうよ。あなたは世界サイテー。\r\nサイテー、サイテー、サイテー……。",
            "enText": "Yes. You are the world's absolute weakest. \nWeakest, weakest, weakest…",
            "nextBlock": 35,
            "origClipLength": 222,
            "voiceIdx": 32,
            "pathId": 3692018134981725298,
            "blockIdx": 34
        },
        {
            "jpName": "エルコンドルパサー",
            "enName": "El Condor Pasa",
            "jpText": "サイテー、サイテー……。もう……ダメです……。\r\nエルは……立ち直れません……。",
            "enText": "The weakest, the weakest… I give up… \nI can't bounce back from this…",
            "nextBlock": 36,
            "origClipLength": 263,
            "voiceIdx": 33,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 308,
                    "pathId": 2614943761312111033
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 305,
                    "pathId": -6495133745872189830
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 332,
                    "pathId": 3568949649489862102
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": 340852111637925307
